name: Synthcity Streets - EP 2: Rescuing Reggie - Standard Edition
description: *Please play in Full Screen for the best experience* // Welcome back to Synthcity, Reggie was captured by a small crime syndicate known as the HEN House. Do you have what it takes to get her back safely? Play the second episode of Synthcity Streets and try your hand at taking back the streets of Synthcity! //  Standard Edition //  Controls - Arrow keys to move, Z,X,C for punch, kick and block. Space to jump, ESC, Enter and left click to navigate menus and cutscenes //  Please use a desktop browser - Works with Chrome, MS Edge,  Brave doesn’t seem to like WebGLs however //  Thank you for playing Synthcity Streets, please consider purchasing the game to help fund future episodes | @Discowarlock on twitter, dm any questions or bugs
